How to reject auto update and update notification of Opera Browser

Opera 68.0.3618.125

Disable the task scheduler libraries "Opera scheduled Autoupdate ***" and "Opera scheduled assistant Autoupdate ***".
Remove files opera_autoupdate.exe, opera_autoupdate.licenses, opera_autoupdate.version in C:\Program Files\Opera\[version]\.
Back up these files if you will update Opera someday.

If you find the file C:\Program Files\Opera\launcher.exe.backup, remove the current launcher.exe and rename the .backup to launcher.exe.
